
login.py is the log in module

Persist.py is the persistence which is using shelve to set up database in order to store the data

1.  Set up a new directory.

2.  Input the command "python3 -m venv demo" to create a virtual environment

3.  Then activate the virtual environment by typing "source demo/bin/activate"

4.  Install Flask by using pip "pip3 install flask"

5.  Get ready
